quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  42,30,"Kala ko heЙ“i on e masiibo, ko sabu ko juuЙ—e mon Й—en faggitii kon. Himo yaafoo non, ko Й—uuЙ—i"
  42,31,"On wonaali laawotooЙ“e ka leydi ; alanaa on gaanin Allah, giЙ—o, wanaa ballo"
  42,32,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko Й—in: dogayЙ—e Й—en ka maayo, wa'uЙ—e wa pelle"
  42,33,"Si O haajii, O deeЖҙinay henndu ndun, ndu waЙ—tinira tabitndu e hoore maggo. Wonii e Й—um, maandeeji, wonannde kala muГұГұotooЙ—o, yettoowo"
  42,34,Maa yooliraЙ—e sabu ko Й“e faggitii kon. Himo yaafoo non ko Й—uuЙ—i
  42,35,"WennjooЙ“e Й“en e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, hino anndi Й“e alaa laaworde"
  42,36,"Kala ko okkaЙ—on e huunde, ko dakamme nguurndam aduna; ko ko woni ka Allah kon, Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude woni kadi ko heddotoo wonannde gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en fawotooЙ“e e Joomi maЙ“Й“e"
  42,37,"woЙ—Й—itotooЙ“e bakkaatuuji mawЙ—i Й—in e pankare Й—en, si wonii Й“e tikkii, hara Й“e yaafoto"
  42,38,"Й“en nootiiЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e ГұiЙ“ni julde nden, Й“e tawata fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e on ko diisondiral hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, nafqooЙ“e e kon ko Men arsiki Й“e"
  42,39,"e Й“en tawЙ“e si bewre heЙ“ii Й“e, Й“e yottoto"
  42,40,"NjoЙ“di bonnere, ko bone yeru mun. Kala non yaafiiЙ—o o moЖҙЖҙintini, haray njoЙ“di makko ndin ko ka Allah woni. Pellet non, O yiЙ—aa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  42,41,"Kala non yottiiЙ“e Й“aawo Й“e tooГұeede, ko Й“en woni Й“e laawol [nanngitireede] fawaaki e mun"
  42,42,"Ko laawol [nanngitireede] fawii e mun, ko tooГұooЙ“e yimЙ“e Й“en, hara hiЙ“e bewira e leydi ndin ko aldaa e goonga: Й“e Й—on, hino woodani lepte muusuЙ—e"
  42,43,"MuГұГұiiЙ—o on kadi o yaafii, ko pellet, Й—um no jeyaa e pellital fiyakuujI"